Main package for AALSpace Gateway.

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Exporter
    Tracks BusMember through the IBusMemberRegistry, when a new BusMember is registered it is checked if it should be exported, through the exporting operation chain, and if it should then it sends all active sessions an import request.
    Gateway
    Main Class for the AALSpace Gateway.
    Importer
    In charge of interpreting import requests coming from remote peer, and associating a local proxy to the request.
